NAME
    exists_function - check to see if a function exists in an object
 
SYNOPSIS
    #include <acme.h>
    static inherit AcmeFunction;
    #include AcmeFunctionInc

    string exists_function( mixed ob, string func );
 
DESCRIPTION
    This is the same as function_exists(), but with the arguments
    reversed so it can be used in a closure (and it accepts filenames
    too).
 
SEE_ALSO
    function_exists(E)
 
LAST MODIFIED
    980102 Devo
